sources.description:
With an Angel on His Shoulder...And the Devil in His Heart!
The Devil arranges for a deceased gangster to return to Earth as a well-respected judge to make up for his previous life.

Director: Archie Mayo
Writers: Harry Segall, Roland Kibbee
Stars: Paul Muni, Anne Baxter, Claude Rains
Genres: Adventure, Comedy, Fantasy, Romance, Film-Noir

Original title: Angel on My Shoulder (1946)
New Colorized version: https://youtu.be/wY8Pc212bSA
